  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Just a short walk from the centre of Sorrento with views across the Bay of Naples, the Hotel Rivage is a great base for exploring the area. It's got a rooftop swimming pool, poolside bar and a restaurant serving Neapolitan cuisine. </p>]]></listingDescription>
